{"tid":1641081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[搵仔]千祈唔好咁做！","createTime":"2019-10-09T08:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T08:41:08.000Z","uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a97cb6096cca66be64d4cdf61adfc9eb30830c9","tid":1641081,"uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:38:48.000Z","msg":"代友Po<br />\n<br />\n收到風popo而家好怕有人上去選舉事務處查選民登記冊起底<br />\n選舉事務處有本實體選民登記冊, 可以比公眾查<br />\n本身係查種票<br />\n一查就所有人都起晒<br />\n如果有popo名，上去查popo地址就...千祈唔好咁做啊！！！<br />\n名就上政府 directory 睇HKPF<br />\n<br />\n查閱正式選民登記冊的地點<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/insp_location.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Finsp_location.htm&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNg8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=9b2eeb10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/insp_location.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash; disclaimer &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n&quot;根據《選舉管理委員會（選民登記）（立法會地方選區）（區議會選區）規例》（第541A章）第22(3)條和《選舉管理委員會（登記）（立法會功能界別選民）（選舉委員會界別分組投票人）（選舉委員會委員）規例》（第541B章）第42(3)條，任何人如非為與選舉有關的目的自行或准許他人以任何形式複製，自行或准許他人使用，或給與任何其他人登記冊內的資料，均屬違法，可處第2級罰款及監禁6個月。&quot;"},{"pid":"691fc7baf6feefbea9e83a8fa6372448f3762d43","tid":1641081,"uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"9e0e7e5a775ab856341b7f4d3ec440a0b37e6eb7","tid":1641081,"uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:39:14.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"0c362951364a9069f50578c6afde8f7d98d9fa12","tid":1641081,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3PNSB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3PNSB7.png&h=70fa4b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4UBLW8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4UBLW8.png&h=10505b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"85d27187038dd31bf9c133a76854da2524913efb","tid":1641081,"uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:39:28.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"b2be2ce11c63469b15f99efbea55fc6159546571","tid":1641081,"uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"664fc424698ee5f7c4cec2b5d827ef73fd11e49f","tid":1641081,"uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:39:53.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"4a400ca1ec651e41343b5b6984a93d46d42b02a2","tid":1641081,"uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:40:09.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"786b08a4ad4fd9b55b9d404e93879cd6a112ee89","tid":1641081,"uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"8cf36853ed217ff2450143b97af35156fa7d91cf","tid":1641081,"uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:40:37.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"ef08b43c5b1cfafe68f7a946f1ac21962e03a8da","tid":1641081,"uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:40:56.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"01d078c511a866ed420e06a3787d51b1f217dd22","tid":1641081,"uid":320043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:41:08.000Z","msg":"10/10"}]}